snippet.title: Urusei Yatsura - Endless Summer Advertisement
snippet.description:
A television advertisement for the Nintendo DS game Urusei Yatsura Endless Summer. The song in the ad is "Star" by Koda Kumi.

You can read more about Urusei Yatsura video games at:
https://furinkan.com/uy/misc/videogames.html
